reviewText: Got as a gift for my niece - She loves it.
What a grate pick  I love the movies  sound clear looked grate  what a triple play  I love my  order thanks
I have always loved almost all the movies she has been in.  She is an excellent actress and should be in more movies.  She is so versatile in everything she does.
Couldn't be happier to receive this triple feature; very fine bargain.  This is the very best of Whoopi, in my opinion.
